{"tid":368783,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"新手旅行用廣角鏡","createTime":"2017-08-21T20:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T00:24:21.000Z","uid":115398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f17d408ffd01cf17546b3c59dea19e33fbfb1033","tid":368783,"uid":115398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T20:15:33.000Z","msg":"大家好<br />\n小弟攝影新手<br />\n用緊多年700d,鍾意影風景<br />\n因最近想旅行時想影風景建築廣d，闊d <br />\n而買一支廣角鏡<br />\n睇左幾隻鏡既資料<br />\nCanon10-18 4.5/5.5<br />\nCanon10-22 3.5/4.5<br />\nSigma10-29 恆定3.5<br />\n請問各位高手，邊隻鏡適合新手用？謝謝"},{"pid":"8d7de203df458fcde2ab19c5c9ad932cfae13f56","tid":368783,"uid":33483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T20:34:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家好<br />\n小弟攝影新手<br />\n用緊多年700d,鍾意影風景<br />\n因最近想旅行時想影風景建築廣d，闊d <br />\n而買一支廣角鏡<br />\n睇左幾隻鏡既資料<br />\nCanon10-18 4.5/5.5<br />\nCanon10-22 3.5/4.5<br />\nSigma10-29 恆定3.5<br />\n請問各位高手，邊隻鏡適合新手用？謝謝</blockquote><br />\n我實支持原廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇你要平定要質素囉"},{"pid":"0c3748eb7881616a320932f1f26b227f18fd4605","tid":368783,"uid":20535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T01:54:43.000Z","msg":"Canon10-22 3.5/4.5 二手價抵啦<br />\n不過如果打算將來升FF就不了"},{"pid":"c26c67aef52bfad68d7a4074b5ea092cfcca9047","tid":368783,"uid":115398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T03:33:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大家好<br />\n小弟攝影新手<br />\n用緊多年700d,鍾意影風景<br />\n因最近想旅行時想影風景建築廣d，闊d <br />\n而買一支廣角鏡<br />\n睇左幾隻鏡既資料<br />\nCanon10-18 4.5/5.5<br />\nCanon10-22 3.5/4.5<br />\nSigma10-29 恆定3.5<br />\n請問各位高手，邊隻鏡適合新手用？謝謝</blockquote><br />\n我實支持原廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇你要平定要質素囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝意見<br />\n因為上過showroom試過c記兩支都唔錯<br />\n但sigma果支 我諗唔到邊度可以試<br />\n質數更係最靚越好啦<br />\n唔想過幾年升級後悔"},{"pid":"f174a9dc145243742321306957393e7b4d1c9b50","tid":368783,"uid":61703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T03:36:54.000Z","msg":"真係睇你會唔會升FF<br />\n我自己就用760d 用10-18個支平野<br />\n都唔差既，變形個d可接受範圍"},{"pid":"a47250bddbd8d311c6afe89de5b434481e0502f9","tid":368783,"uid":33483,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T03:47:19.000Z","msg":"宜家換埋6d2啦 再加支16-35夠wide<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"594f5091bc8eabfc8c35874424bc89a27e73ae3a","tid":368783,"uid":43545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T03:49:52.000Z","msg":"1022 自己用緊<br />\n性價比高<br />\n好似話停左產定出左第二代"},{"pid":"8baebfe84552b5bf3562b7a129c83b7717bf37f2","tid":368783,"uid":31305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T09:25:14.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n我同你一樣用緊700D<br />\n遲d去旅行想影紅葉<br />\n呢兩支canon都岩心水<br />\n但又有d想買天涯鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10bc1fa928a89609dc53aa874f03367879fb44cc","tid":368783,"uid":70689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T14:03:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名<br />\n我同你一樣用緊700D<br />\n遲d去旅行想影紅葉<br />\n呢兩支canon都岩心水<br />\n但又有d想買天涯鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好買天涯鏡<br />\n我自己覺得都幾差下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw  10-18<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b437c2a5fb406eddf2b3e60f8484410151871d","tid":368783,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T14:23:06.000Z","msg":"10+18唔錯<br />\n變形都唔多覺"},{"pid":"f0205d0ce11b4c2b77005613a81b855254e127b0","tid":368783,"uid":98049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:22:04.000Z","msg":"10-18"},{"pid":"b668ceb72d30b4a3bedc2dae891b9da3b0357114","tid":368783,"uid":115398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:39:25.000Z","msg":"多謝各位巴打意見~<br />\n睇過<br />\nC10-18<br />\nS10-20<br />\nT11-20<br />\n<br />\nTOKINA最差...開盡2.8變牛油紙~對焦好嘈..雖然我唔拍片,嘈唔關我事<br />\nSIGMA開盡3.5都無咁差..對焦都係好嘈"},{"pid":"bcffe9ce7599c91f9c4f541f1a05faeea7a34c3f","tid":368783,"uid":17166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T07:27:59.000Z","msg":"C10-18 真心輕便，1900蚊真係無投訴<br />\n要來去旅行真係一流，特別係歐洲，因為啲建築物好大，真係唔係蹆後一步就影到。<br />\n<br />\n不過咁，支鏡係暗嘅情況下真係可以收得皮。試過有次去森林，天氣麻麻加上啲樹好高，影出嚟好多張都唔要得，除非用1600iso以上，但可想而知啲質素會好差<br />\n<br />\n利申:用緊700D+c10-18+s17-50"},{"pid":"b5a048da1c9f70b413400cb3d5de6f1040d7380e","tid":368783,"uid":81756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:12:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>C10-18 真心輕便，1900蚊真係無投訴<br />\n要來去旅行真係一流，特別係歐洲，因為啲建築物好大，真係唔係蹆後一步就影到。<br />\n<br />\n不過咁，支鏡係暗嘅情況下真係可以收得皮。試過有次去森林，天氣麻麻加上啲樹好高，影出嚟好多張都唔要得，除非用1600iso以上，但可想而知啲質素會好差<br />\n<br />\n利申:用緊700D+c10-18+s17-50</blockquote><br />\n影景落腳架咪得 下下手持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8862a4083e9f9b4f97503de41f3f56403e3d0e26","tid":368783,"uid":117044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:24:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec8c1ae9b37ad7d152db4aa0302fa371be55914e","tid":368783,"uid":117044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:38:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a0849f3f05ad7b3351529d29892e474ea25574e","tid":368783,"uid":9315,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T15:10:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>C10-18 真心輕便，1900蚊真係無投訴<br />\n要來去旅行真係一流，特別係歐洲，因為啲建築物好大，真係唔係蹆後一步就影到。<br />\n<br />\n不過咁，支鏡係暗嘅情況下真係可以收得皮。試過有次去森林，天氣麻麻加上啲樹好高，影出嚟好多張都唔要得，除非用1600iso以上，但可想而知啲質素會好差<br />\n<br />\n利申:用緊700D+c10-18+s17-50</blockquote><br />\n影景落腳架咪得 下下手持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去旅行呀大哥  下下同你企定定慢慢set腳架?<br />\n自己去唔介意都還好<br />\n有伴既話你要對方睇住你下下又開又摺?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb52d9ee1fab927791b4685ed658c06022f61f4a","tid":368783,"uid":104387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T15:59:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>C10-18 真心輕便，1900蚊真係無投訴<br />\n要來去旅行真係一流，特別係歐洲，因為啲建築物好大，真係唔係蹆後一步就影到。<br />\n<br />\n不過咁，支鏡係暗嘅情況下真係可以收得皮。試過有次去森林，天氣麻麻加上啲樹好高，影出嚟好多張都唔要得，除非用1600iso以上，但可想而知啲質素會好差<br />\n<br />\n利申:用緊700D+c10-18+s17-50</blockquote><br />\n你想講你收皮定支鏡收皮定部機收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8129479ad05fd76b475b19f06efb6cb4e31d8f5d","tid":368783,"uid":78888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T16:19:18.000Z","msg":"Nikon 機用邊支好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f5809240cc60a977f84fa2bbd1faee4f2fe472","tid":368783,"uid":27358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T23:50:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Nikon 機用邊支好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nT116<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dba9604cbc595e7fec36d9c4037277492638e24","tid":368783,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T01:09:18.000Z","msg":"tokina 11-16/2.8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e0039238ee02f0feadec8f4c82a1f120f592050","tid":368783,"uid":78888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T01:15:03.000Z","msg":"咁tokina11-20係咪好d?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"524373de8fe9829dbbe72ab32181845c78c98619","tid":368783,"uid":33777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T03:58:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Nikon 機用邊支好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nT116<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nT124 2代係咪比T116 2代唔好?"},{"pid":"05eada1a5b2543c2d8f9fbd30f00ba4535ce07e2","tid":368783,"u